{"about_the_game":"&quot;<i>First Step</i>&quot; is a short demo for the upcoming &quot;Dropkick Navvy&quot;, designed to help us fine-tune the fun.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530500/extras/NG-Steam-Header-01-About.png?t=1729020123\" /><br><br>Do you dig crafting games like <i>Minecraft</i>, <i>Astroneer</i>, and <i>Forager</i>? How about goofy physics sims like <i>Human: Fall Flat</i> or <i>Moving Out</i>?<br><br>We love both \u2014 so we smushed em together!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530500/extras/FunGIF.gif?t=1729020123\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530500/extras/NG-Steam-Header-02-Features.png?t=1729020123\" /><br><br>Go ham on rocks and trees with slapdash tools you made yourself, then pile \u2018em into your little wicker basket and wobble back to your workbench in charmingly precarious fashion. <br><br>Or just dropkick them suckers clear across the map. Ain't nobody got time for all that.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530500/extras/GatherGIF.gif?t=1729020123\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Roam the cosmos and knock down everything in your path to turn them into stuff! <br></li><li>Can\u2019t hold all the stuff? Try throwing it or using a basket or something! </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530500/extras/CraftGIF2.gif?t=1729020123\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Craft some tools! And then craft some more tools! And keep crafting until you run out! <br></li><li>Then use those tools to help you gather more stuff to craft even more tools. Oh, and workbenches too! </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530500/extras/LevelUpGIF2.gif?t=1729020123\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Don\u2019t forget the Growth Potions. Craft some of those and throw them at the World Tree! <br></li><li>Watch the World Tree grow taller! So tall that you might need a little boost to reach its branches! </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530500/extras/ExpandGIF.gif?t=1729020123\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Expand, expand, expand, until you can\u2019t expand anymore! <br></li><li>New lands, new materials, new puzzles just waiting to be revealed! </li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530500/0be5e7993376e8e3e1bd614e038a3b3a2629b5d6.jpg"},{"name":"First Build","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530500/386a4ac100b8cc47e3f6d1982281c04d4cbaff76.jpg"},{"name":"The Giving Tree","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530500/5bf6898b81167a7cdd33c5538f41d2bcf0a81699.jpg"},{"name":"Where's My Diamond Pickaxe?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530500/76f2ab754845761fb9fd3dd6ff11ec0aaef7b2cb.jpg"},{"name":"Blue Margarita","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530500/96c147d2258a90bd62f6c5e27dd904663c9a719b.jpg"},{"name":"The Invention of Basketball","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530500/c21fb53db4ee0b9a899b07d765f14946b4f8f408.jpg"},{"name":"Workers Unite!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530500/d2bd14ea9543f486cd8aea06c9b945bd45bf6495.jpg"},{"name":"Enormivis!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530500/78f505ddded558ec61d48bfe8a6f0525532544f2.jpg"},{"name":"Reaper of Souls","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/